    "description": "Asian Paints is actively seeking a talented and motivated Manufacturing Engineer to join our dynamic team in Patna. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Asian Paints:\nAsian Paints is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement 5S, Kaizen, and Six Sigma practices on the shop floor\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Train and supervise shop floor workers and supervisors\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Implement lean manufacturing and continuous improvement initiatives\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in GD&T\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in Root Cause Analysis\n• Proficiency in Statistical Process Control\n• Proficiency in PLC/SCADA\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Referral bonus program\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Asian Paints!",
